# Seismo Live Production Environment

## Tech Stack & Environment

- **OS:** Ubuntu 26.04 LTS (Hetzner Cloud VPS)
- **Language stack:** PHP 8.5 (strict typing, modern OOP)
- **Web server:** Nginx (`fastcgi_read_timeout` = 300s)
- **Database:** MariaDB via Unix socket; database name `seismo`
- **App root:** `/var/www/seismo` (owner `www-data:www-data`)

## Deployment & Ops

- Deploy remotely via Git or SFTP to **116.202.99.217**.
- Scripts that write logs must use standard locations: project `storage/logs/` or `/var/log/nginx/` so monitoring agents can parse them.
- When suggesting server commands, paths, or Nginx/PHP-FPM config, assume this VPS layout—not shared webhosting.
